"title": "5815: confusion",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5815: confusion",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of perplexity, bewilderment or disorder. Confusion may be brought about by God to cause the schemes of the wicked to fail and opposition to his people to prove ineffective. Confusion over spiritual truth is the natural state of humanity; believers, too, may be perplexed by God's purposes or thrown into confusion by false teaching.</p>\n<h2>Examples of people in confusion</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:29\">2SA 18:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:15\">EST 3:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:25-Luke21:26\">LUK 21:25–21:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:8\">ACT 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:32\">ACT 19:32</a></p>\n<h2>God sends confusion as judgment</h2>\n<h3>The righteous ask God to confuse their enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:26\">PSA 35:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:14\">PSA 40:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:9\">PSA 55:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps70:2\">PSA 70:2</a></p>\n<h3>God sends confusion on Israel's enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:27\">EXO 23:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:23\">DEU 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:24\">PSA 71:24</a></p>\n<h3>Israel, too, may experience confusion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:20\">DEU 28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:28\">DEU 28:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:5-2Chr15:6\">2CH 15:5–15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:34\">JER 51:34</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of God sending confusion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:7-Gen11:9\">GEN 11:7–11:9</a> <em>at the tower of Babel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:10\">JOS 10:10</a> <em>on the Amorites</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:20\">1SA 14:20</a> <em>on the Philistines</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:22-2Chr20:23\">2CH 20:22–20:23</a> <em>on Jehoshaphat's enemies</em></p>\n<h2>Spiritual confusion is humanity's natural state</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:29\">ISA 41:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:3-2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:3–4:4</a></p>\n<h2>Confusion relating to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Confusion among the Jews</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:52\">JHN 6:52</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:6-Acts2:7\">ACT 2:6–2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:23-Matt12:24\">MAT 12:23–12:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:22\">MRK 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:15\">LUK 11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:7-Luke9:9\">LUK 9:7–9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:1-Matt14:2\">MAT 14:1–14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:14-Mark6:16\">MRK 6:14–6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:4\">JHN 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:12\">ACT 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14\">2CO 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Confusion among Jesus Christ's disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:27\">MAT 8:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:41\">MRK 4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:25\">LUK 8:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:5-Mark9:6\">MRK 9:5–9:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:4\">MAT 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:33-Luke9:34\">LUK 9:33–9:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:8\">MRK 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:22-Luke24:25\">LUK 24:22–24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:60\">JHN 6:60</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:17-John16:19\">JHN 16:17–16:19</a></p>\n<h2>Further examples of believers in confusion</h2>\n<h3>Confusion over God's purposes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:8\">2CO 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:12-Ps73:14\">PSA 73:12–73:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:15\">ECC 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:3-Isa21:4\">ISA 21:3–21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:19\">DAN 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2-Hab1:4\">HAB 1:2–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:5\">2CO 7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19-Gal4:20\">GAL 4:19–4:20</a></p>\n<h3>Confusion over doctrine</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:7\">GAL 1:6–1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:9\">GAL 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:17\">GAL 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:10\">GAL 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Remedies for confusion</h2>\n<h3>Confusion dispelled by asking God for understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:3\">JER 33:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Confusion dispelled by the enlightenment of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9-1Cor2:10\">1CO 2:9–2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Confusion combated by the teaching of wise leaders</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28-Acts20:30\">ACT 20:28–20:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:24-2Tim2:25\">2TI 2:24–2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2-2Tim4:3\">2TI 4:2–4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></p>\n<h3>Confusion dispelled by the instruction of Scripture</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:103-Ps119:105\">PSA 119:103–119:105</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Confusion goes as believers grow to spiritual maturity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13-Eph4:14\">EPH 4:13–4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:10\">PHP 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:14\">HEB 5:14</a></p>",
